    <ThingDef ParentName="DankPyon_LootBase">
        <defName>DankPyon_Book_TheBeginning</defName>
        <label>the beginning</label>
        <description>The Beginning
            \nA survival guide into the wilderness
            \n\n1.Hides and Leather
            \nUsuable leather can be obtained by treating hides with tanning liquor in a tanning rack.
             After waiting an ample amount of time, the treated leather is ready for use
            
            \n\n2.Where is my food 
            \nFresh meat spoils fast, better act quick! Meat can be preserved by putting them in drying racks, prolonging their expected shelf life.
             Later on, packaged rations or the vegetarian alternative, macci, can be made to eliminate any problem of spoilage.
             
             \n\n3.Metallurgy \nGood swords need good iron, refining raw metal ores is neccessary to make weapons. 
             Raw ores can be smelt on the furnace to produce ingots that can be used for crafting and smithing.</description>
        <graphicData>
            <texPath>Special/TheBeginning</texPath>
            <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
        </graphicData>

         <statBases>
            <MaxHitPoints>70</MaxHitPoints>
            <MarketValue>150</MarketValue>
            <Beauty>0</Beauty>
            <Mass>1</Mass>
            <Flammability>0</Flammability>
            <DeteriorationRate>1.0</DeteriorationRate>
        </statBases>

        <costList>
            <DankPyon_Paper>50</DankPyon_Paper>
        </costList>
    </ThingDef>


